creator: NCKO
descriptionHtml:
North Carolina Kenyans Organization (NCKO) is a team of energized group working to support and inspire each other to achieve their potential whilst giving utmost welfare support. The mission of NCKO as a Non-Profit Organization is to bring together Kenyans living in North Carolina and improve their social-economic wellbeing while availing assistance to all NCKO
members at their time of need.
